nhc_headline: ...IMELDA LIKELY TO BE A HURRICANE NEAR BERMUDA LATE ON WEDNESDAY...
summary: ...IMELDA LIKELY TO BE A HURRICANE NEAR BERMUDA LATE ON WEDNESDAY... As of 5:00 AM EDT Tue Sep 30 the center of Imelda was located near 28.8, -76.8 with movement NE at 7 mph. The minimum central pressure was 981 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 70 mph.
